HARIPUR, Dec 22 (APP): The funeral prayer of Subedar Major Khurshid Akram was offered at his native village Jabbi Bakka, Kot Najibullah, in Haripur.
He was martyred by terrorists on Wednesday after he was made hostage in a compound in Bannu cantonment.Earlier, guard of honour was presented to the Shaheed by the army personnel.
